WEBVTT

00:05.120 --> 00:09.000
<i>♪ The war is over now ♪</i>

00:10.320 --> 00:14.400
<i>♪ And it's quiet all around ♪</i>

00:15.000 --> 00:16.120
It's late.

00:18.040 --> 00:19.400
I'm going to bed.

00:19.480 --> 00:20.640
[chuckles softly]

00:22.440 --> 00:25.640
-What are you doing there?
-I could stay like this all night.

00:25.720 --> 00:29.160
That's because you're the boss
and you don't have to get up early.

00:29.240 --> 00:32.680
<i>♪ That I feel peaceful ♪</i>

00:34.480 --> 00:35.800
<i>♪ Peaceful ♪</i>

00:35.880 --> 00:37.280
[Alba] <i>Future or past.</i>

00:38.160 --> 00:40.400
<i>We all have to decide</i>
<i>at some point in our life</i>

00:40.480 --> 00:42.400
<i>which way we want to look.</i>

00:44.480 --> 00:46.000
<i>If you want to cling to the past,</i>

00:46.080 --> 00:47.960
<i>to stick with what you already know,</i>

00:48.680 --> 00:52.080
<i>or if you want to leave it behind</i>
<i>and look toward the future.</i>

00:52.160 --> 00:53.680
[Alba laughing]

00:56.360 --> 00:58.800
<i>The future is scary sometimes</i>
<i>because it's unknown.</i>

00:58.880 --> 01:01.400
[whispering] Go home. Go on.

01:01.920 --> 01:04.080
<i>But it's also more exciting,</i>

01:04.160 --> 01:07.240
<i>and it can make your heart beat</i>
<i>in ways you forgot it could.</i>

01:07.320 --> 01:12.720
<i>♪ And I feel peaceful ♪</i>

01:13.400 --> 01:15.920
[Carolina] "I'll always love you, Alba."

01:16.000 --> 01:19.560
<i>♪ I feel peaceful ♪</i>

01:19.640 --> 01:20.800
[door opening]

01:24.840 --> 01:26.640
-[gasps]
-So Don Carlos, eh?

01:26.720 --> 01:28.040
You kept that quiet.

01:28.120 --> 01:30.600
You scared me. What are you doing here?

01:30.680 --> 01:32.440
I couldn't sleep.

01:32.520 --> 01:35.840
I got up for a glass of warm milk,
and I heard you two arriving.

01:35.920 --> 01:37.600
It isn't like I was looking out
the window.

01:37.680 --> 01:40.640
Well, yes, I was... but just a little.

01:42.040 --> 01:43.720
[softly] I'm going to bed.

01:43.800 --> 01:46.480
Lidia, I get it. Carlos is very handsome.

01:46.560 --> 01:48.840
He doesn't have
my Pablo's curly hair, but--

01:48.920 --> 01:52.200
[Alba] So now he's "your Pablo"?
Do you have something to tell me?

01:53.200 --> 01:55.080
[Marga] Lidia, don't change the subject.

01:55.160 --> 01:56.880
-Good evening.
-Good evening, girls.

01:56.960 --> 01:59.640
What are you doing here?
Your room's in the other hall.

01:59.720 --> 02:02.920
Oh, strange.
I didn't know I had to answer to you.

02:05.560 --> 02:08.000
That girl's like an infected bunion.

02:08.080 --> 02:09.600
[Carlota] Why didn't you tell me?

02:11.280 --> 02:13.440
You didn't think twice about lying to me.

02:13.520 --> 02:14.840
[Miguel] You're scolding me for that?

02:14.920 --> 02:18.040
Normally, the best defense
is a good offense, but not this time.

02:18.120 --> 02:20.240
My being there was the least of it!
You were kissing!

02:20.320 --> 02:22.840
I thought we told each other everything,
that we weren't like everyone else.

02:22.920 --> 02:25.080
-And we're not.
-Are you sure? Look at us!

02:27.760 --> 02:29.000
Carlota...

02:31.000 --> 02:33.880
-if you don't love me anymore...
-Miguel, I love you.

02:34.600 --> 02:36.000
Then what's this about?

02:41.440 --> 02:42.320
I don't know.

02:47.560 --> 02:49.800
Let's talk this over somewhere else,
like your place.

02:51.200 --> 02:52.240
That'd be better.

02:53.360 --> 02:55.720
But I'm going. I need to be alone.

02:55.800 --> 02:58.720
Miguel, please. Please, wait!

03:01.880 --> 03:03.280
<i>♪ I wanted love the most ♪</i>

03:03.360 --> 03:06.040
A NETFLIX ORIGINAL SERIES

03:06.120 --> 03:08.520
<i>♪ But it never stays long ♪</i>

03:09.960 --> 03:16.640
<i>♪ A notch to my bedpost</i>
<i>Pretend they're mine ♪</i>

03:17.800 --> 03:21.720
<i>♪ Sundress wrinkled on the floor</i>
<i>I'm naked, you're not here no more ♪</i>

03:21.800 --> 03:24.480
<i>♪ To keep me warm, keep me warm ♪</i>

03:25.840 --> 03:29.560
<i>♪ Crack the door with a trash bin</i>
<i>Maybe you will come back in ♪</i>

03:29.640 --> 03:32.720
<i>♪ And keep me warm, keep me warm ♪</i>

03:34.000 --> 03:38.480
<i>♪ My love, my love, my love ♪</i>

03:39.400 --> 03:45.200
<i>♪ Pour salt in the wound ♪</i>

03:46.040 --> 03:50.360
<i>♪ My love, my love, my love ♪</i>

03:50.920 --> 03:56.760
<i>♪ Pour salt in the wound ♪</i>

04:02.360 --> 04:04.960
-So you broke up?
-No. Well, I'm not sure.

04:05.040 --> 04:07.600
I just want him to understand me
and forgive me.

04:07.680 --> 04:09.560
For what? What happened, Carlota?

04:10.160 --> 04:12.400
-Marga.
-What happened?

04:12.480 --> 04:14.320
I've started having feelings...

04:16.440 --> 04:18.519
-for someone else.
-You don't love Miguel anymore?

04:18.600 --> 04:20.240
No, I didn't say that.

04:20.320 --> 04:23.160
I just think you can have feelings
for two people at the same time.

04:23.240 --> 04:25.320
[Marga] Really? Can you?

04:28.200 --> 04:29.240
Hold on...

04:31.160 --> 04:32.000
What's wrong?

04:38.040 --> 04:41.200
CHAPTER 5: THE PAST

04:41.280 --> 04:43.840
Someone came in here
and went through my things.

04:43.920 --> 04:46.240
Lola must have moved things
while she was cleaning.

04:49.840 --> 04:52.560
No, it was her.

04:54.240 --> 04:55.640
[banging on door]

04:57.400 --> 05:00.040
-You went through my things!
-I'm not interested in your things.

05:00.120 --> 05:01.880
What? Are you scared I'll find something?

05:01.960 --> 05:04.680
-You should be more careful.
-What's this fuss about?

05:04.760 --> 05:07.040
It's very late,
and this is a decent house.

05:07.120 --> 05:10.000
-What's going on?
-Were we making a lot of noise?

05:10.080 --> 05:13.600
Sorry, we were having so much fun
in Carolina's room

05:13.680 --> 05:15.560
that we lost track of time. I'm sorry.

05:15.640 --> 05:18.920
-Yes, so much fun.
-Don't worry. It won't happen again.

05:19.000 --> 05:21.560
Anyway, we were saying good night,
weren't we?

05:21.640 --> 05:22.840
[Alba] Yeah.

05:22.920 --> 05:27.960
I like that you're getting along,
but maybe get along at a decent hour.

05:28.040 --> 05:32.640
Don't forget:
early to bed, early to rise...

05:36.760 --> 05:38.080
Good night.

05:44.160 --> 05:45.960
[Carlota] It's a suitcase.
Who'd be interested in it?

05:46.040 --> 05:48.840
There are private things in it
that don't just concern me.

05:48.920 --> 05:50.440
-Who else?
-It's none of your business.

05:50.520 --> 05:51.600
She's right.

05:52.640 --> 05:55.200
Lidia, if you won't trust us,
we can't help you.

05:55.280 --> 05:57.920
-She's right, too.
-He's a married man.

05:58.920 --> 06:00.520
Good Lord, what's going on today?

06:00.600 --> 06:02.680
It's over between us,

06:02.760 --> 06:06.320
but if people find out about it,
it'll mean trouble.

06:07.560 --> 06:08.960
[sighs heavily]

06:09.040 --> 06:12.040
That suitcase is proof of my past,
a past that I don't want back.

06:12.120 --> 06:14.640
Like your village or your family.
I hope you understand.

06:14.720 --> 06:16.400
Yes, we understand.

06:17.280 --> 06:19.280
But knowing Carolina, she won't stop.

06:19.360 --> 06:22.280
If you want to resolve this,
you'll have to get rid of that suitcase.

06:22.360 --> 06:23.560
Even if it hurts.

06:25.640 --> 06:27.600
[upbeat music playing]

06:31.720 --> 06:33.840
I've located the blueprints
for the prototype.

06:33.920 --> 06:36.240
So what's wrong?
I thought that would make you happy.

06:36.320 --> 06:39.320
[Alba] I can't steal them
until it's built and it works.

06:39.400 --> 06:40.560
As of now, they're worthless.

06:40.640 --> 06:45.800
I guess you'll have to be patient
and spend more time with the rich kid.

06:45.880 --> 06:46.880
Hmm?

06:51.480 --> 06:53.120
Is that what worries you?

06:54.760 --> 06:56.760
You're afraid of getting too close to him?

06:59.560 --> 07:01.480
Alba, honey, look at me.

07:04.960 --> 07:06.040
Do you like him?

07:06.840 --> 07:09.080
-Did something happen between you?
-Victoria, please!

07:09.760 --> 07:10.880
What's this about?

07:11.800 --> 07:14.840
If you're developing feelings for him,

07:14.920 --> 07:17.720
you'd better stop all of this right away.

07:17.800 --> 07:20.520
-You know what happens when we mix--
-Will you stop?

07:21.440 --> 07:23.240
Carlos has nothing to do with this.

07:24.480 --> 07:26.160
What I'm worried about is Beltrán...

07:28.240 --> 07:30.800
and that what happened between Francisco
and I will be exposed.

07:33.200 --> 07:35.800
<i>♪ Is this moment real ♪</i>

07:35.880 --> 07:38.200
[Alba] <i>That was the most important thing</i>
<i>back then:</i>

07:39.800 --> 07:44.200
<i>that my past wouldn't be revealed...</i>
<i>and that nobody would find out...</i>

07:45.800 --> 07:49.560
<i>because the past can leave marks</i>
<i>that are impossible to erase,</i>

07:53.880 --> 07:57.000
<i>marks that you know will be</i>
<i>with you your whole life,</i>

07:57.080 --> 07:59.360
<i>every time you rest your head</i>
<i>on the pillow.</i>

08:04.040 --> 08:07.400
<i>Some marks remind you</i>
<i>where you wanted to be,</i>

08:09.280 --> 08:12.120
<i>while others remind you</i>
<i>where you never want to be again,</i>

08:14.600 --> 08:16.760
<i>but at least those can be covered up.</i>

